{"word":"H1530 - גַּל - gal - gal - Billow","slug":"H1530","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גַּל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>gal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>gal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Billow"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05DC; - gal</b> - <i>gal</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H1556\">H1556</a>; something <i>rolled</i>, that is, a <i>heap</i> of stone or dung (plural <i>ruins</i>); by analogy a <i>spring</i> of water (plural <i>waves</i>): - billow, heap, spring, wave."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1019\">H1019</a>, <a href=\"#/H1531\">H1531</a>, <a href=\"#/H1534\">H1534</a>, <a href=\"#/H1536\">H1536</a>, <a href=\"#/H1537\">H1537</a>, <a href=\"#/H1538\">H1538</a>, <a href=\"#/H1543\">H1543</a>, <a href=\"#/H1544\">H1544</a>, <a href=\"#/H1550\">H1550</a>, <a href=\"#/H1551\">H1551</a>, <a href=\"#/H1552\">H1552</a>, <a href=\"#/H1553\">H1553</a>, <a href=\"#/H1554\">H1554</a>, <a href=\"#/H1556\">H1556</a>, <a href=\"#/H1557\">H1557</a>, <a href=\"#/H1559\">H1559</a>, <a href=\"#/H1561\">H1561</a>, <a href=\"#/H1562\">H1562</a>, <a href=\"#/H1567\">H1567</a>, <a href=\"#/H4039\">H4039</a>"}]}